---
title: Beef Cheeseburger Enchiladas with Caramelised Onion & Hidden Veggies
description: Go stateside tonight by adding All-American flavours to a beef filling for enchiladas with a touch of Dijon mustard, so when you
close your eyes, it tastes just like a cheeseburger! Sneak some veggies into the mix, smother the lot with cheese, top it off with sticky
caramelised onion and you're good to go. That's all, folks!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-cheeseburger-enchiladas-2427a233.jpg
